title: quantum computer factorization
extract: Researchers have designed and built a quantum computer from five atoms in an ion trap. The computer uses laser pulses to carry out Shor's algorithm on each atom, to correctly factor the number 15. ... Researchers have designed and built a quantum computer from five atoms in an ion trap.Mar 3, 2016
